# WaveGame GDD - Brothers Multiplayer Survival
Last Update: Nov 2025  
Repo: https://github.com/kschroe3/wavegame

## 1. Overview
- Genre: 1-4 Player Online Wave Survival
- Core Loop: Lobby → Class Select → Survive Waves → Boss Every 10 → Loot → Repeat
- Win: Highest wave reached
- Players: P2P (Host = server)

## 2. Classes
| Class | Strong vs | Weak vs | Color Options |
|-------|-----------|---------|---------------|
| Warrior | Ranged | Magic | Red, Blue, Green, Yellow |
| Wizard | Melee | Ranged | (unique per lobby) |
| Archer | Magic | Melee | |
| Cleric | Healing | All | |

## 3. Rooms
- `rm_main_menu` → Host/Join
- `rm_lobby` → Passcode, player list, class select
- `rm_arena` → Game

